title: Major Upload
body: Includes all of the changes I've been working on the last year. Mostly cosmetic problems and menu structures. The code is now self-contained (unless I missed a test or two), and we can alter it how we want. Several new tests and editing functions have been added. Several menu items have changed, and plots on all tests have been done away with. Correct and more in-depth conclusion paragraphs have been included.
